ent-Z14ZoneArtifactDetectorBarracuda = Barracuda detector
    .desc = Detector assembled from Okhotnik data. It is able to display distance on its screen, which is much more efficient than it was before. It got its name due to the fact that its device was invented while fishing.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14ZoneArtifactDetectorBear = Bear detector
    .desc = Anomalous activity detector, equipped with a directional locator. The artifact search mode is activated by lifting the antenna cover on the front side of the device.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14ZoneArtifactDetectorBush = Bush detector
    .desc = The detector was assembled on the basis of data received from the "Hunter". Able to display distances on your screen, which are much more effective than what was before. It got its name because its device was invented while fishing.
    .suffix = Z14

